 the actuation triggered by a wall shear sensor seems to be\nmore effective than the actuation triggered by a wall pressure sensor, at least\nfor the preliminary definitions of sensors and thresholds used here.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 20 Feb 2020 16:39:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-06-14"}
