act on security properties\nof the consensus protocol. Simulation results validated our analysis. Our\nmodeling and analysis provide a paradigm for assessing the security impact of\nvarious factors in a distributed consensus system.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 20 Feb 2020 17:54:57 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 23 May 2020 18:07:46 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 31 Aug 2020 23:56:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-09-02"}
