l effects. Finally, we use the simulation to\ninvestigate the links between $\\Delta f_q$ and quenching of star formation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 21 Feb 2020 01:32:19 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 30 Mar 2020 02:45:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-03-31"}
