tically, reducing the resources necessary for repositioning. The\nlocalization of dyneins in the pSMAC facilitates their interaction with the\nMTs. Our model also opens a way to infer details of the dynein distribution\nfrom the experimentally observed features of the MT cytoskeleton dynamics. In a\nsubsequent publication, we will address the issue of general initial\nconfigurations and situations in which the T cell established two immunological\nsynapses.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 21 Feb 2020 14:26:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-04-22"}
